      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "LAKEVIEW LEIGH (1) has a fair record and proved too strong last time to win by 0.8 lengths at Sandown in a handy 34.98 beating Parabola. The form from her last run stacks up well. Can continue the winning form. STROP (6) showed little early speed at his last couple, the latest finishing sixth (26.04) in a Grade 4/5 at Shepparton. Solid record at the distance winning two races. Great chance to atone. MILDRED ROSE (7) produced an impressive win last time in quickest of the meeting when scoring by a long neck (29.08) at this track. Harder here but expected to feature again. SKI BOOTS (2) is another with top-three prospects.",
